OL,7,FA teenager's life could have been
OL,8,Fsaved if he had been given "basic"
OL,9,Finstructions by Scout leaders, an
OL,10,Finquest heard.
OL,12,FBen Leonard, 16, from Stockport,
OL,13,FGreater Manchester, was on an
OL,14,Forganised expedition with the Reddish
OL,15,FExplorer Scouts on August 26 2018 when
OL,16,Fhe suffered a serious head injury
OL,17,Fafter falling 200 feet from cliffs on
OL,18,Fthe Great Orme in North Wales.
