OL,3,CTeen's life could have been saved if
OL,4,CScout leaders had given basic
OL,5,Cinstructions
OL,7,FGareth Williams was the first of the
OL,8,Fthree Scout leaders on the trip to
OL,9,Fgive evidence at Ben's inquest, now in
OL,10,Fits fourth week, at Manchester Civil
OL,11,FJustice Centre.
OL,13,FMr Williams, at the time aged 26 and
OL,14,Fan assistant Scout leader, told the
OL,15,Fhearing it was his first trip as a
OL,16,FScout Leader, he had never met Ben
OL,17,Fbefore and he was asked to go because
OL,18,F"I was basically another car to use as
OL,19,Ftransport", he said.
