OL,3,CTeen's life could have been saved if
OL,4,CScout leaders had given basic
OL,5,Cinstructions
OL,7,FMr Williams continued: "Sean got a
OL,8,Fphone call and he turned around and
OL,9,Fsaid, 'Oh you're joking!'. Then I
OL,10,Fremember hearing sirens. I can't
OL,11,Fremember if he said, 'Ben's fallen' or
OL,12,F'Ben's had an accident.'
OL,14,F"After that it just got quite
OL,15,Fpanicked."
OL,17,FHe added: "I have reflected on this
OL,18,Ffor five years. I could not even
OL,19,Fconceive of the possibility they would
OL,20,Fnot re-join the path and try and join
OL,21,Fthe group back up."
