OL,3,CTeen's life could have been saved if
OL,4,CScout leaders had given basic
OL,5,Cinstructions
OL,7,FBernard Richmond KC, representing
OL,8,FBen's family suggested Mr Williams had
OL,9,F"lost" the three boys on the walk up
OL,10,Fthe Orme.
OL,12,FHe said: "I know it's hard but if you
OL,13,Fare a supervising adult, supervising
OL,14,Fothers and you can't see them, you
OL,15,Fhave lost them?"
OL,17,FMr Williams said on occasion Scouts
OL,18,Fwill not always be in sight on
OL,19,Factivities.
