OL,3,CTeen's life could have been saved if
OL,4,CScout leaders had given basic
OL,5,Cinstructions
OL,7,F"No," Mr Williams replied, "I did not
OL,8,Feven anticipate they would go near
OL,9,Fcliffs."
OL,11,FMr Richmond added: "Ben's life would
OL,12,Fhave been saved if somebody said to
OL,13,Fhim, 'This area has to be avoided,
OL,14,Fthese routes are all safe.' That's all
OL,15,Fit would've taken?"
OL,17,F"I think so, I can't know, but I think
OL,18,Fso," Mr Williams said.
