OL,4,CScout leaders had given basic
OL,5,Cinstructions
OL,7,FMr Richmond continued: "Can you think
OL,8,Fof a more basic failure of care Mr
OL,9,FWilliams, short of pushing someone off
OL,10,Fthe cliff yourself? There isn't, is
OL,11,Fthere?"
OL,13,F"I'm not sure," Mr Williams replied.
